      "content": "i'm just saying, i've had people say that once you've taken the first dose it's mostly fine as long as you don't go overboard. like, can't i just take the meds in the morning and then have a drink in the evening? it's not like they stay in my system forever. is there any way to do it safely without skipping the whole thing?",
